"""Test get_headroom."""
headroom_list = self.common.get_headroom(self.conn.array_id)
self.assertTrue(isinstance(headroom_list, list))
for i in range(len(headroom_list)):
    self.assertTrue(set({'emulation': 'CKD'}.items()).issubset(set(
        headroom_list[i].items())) or set({'emulation': 'FBA'}.items()).
        issubset(set(headroom_list[i].items())))
